not remember how they
got back to their room?

24
00:03:07,083 --> 00:03:10,250
Oh wow! The sake gods were
pleased with your drinking.

25
00:03:10,333 --> 00:03:13,041
That's why they carried
you safely back to your room!

26
00:03:13,125 --> 00:03:15,333
That elixir of Guan
Yu's is magic sauce.

27
00:03:15,416 --> 00:03:16,375
That's not what I--

28
00:03:17,166 --> 00:03:18,250
What are you doing?!

29
