I'm telling you, I've
had this machine for years.

32
00:03:24,625 --> 00:03:26,458
I'm the only one who
knows how to use it right.

33
00:03:26,541 --> 00:03:28,291
'Kay now this thing?
I think it goes here...

34
00:03:28,375 --> 00:03:29,833
Don't do that.
You're going to get the

35
00:03:29,916 --> 00:03:31,875
thread completely tangled.

36
00:03:32,458 --> 00:03:33,083
It got all tangled.

37
00:03:33,166 --> 00:03:34,125
I told you!

38
00:03:34,208 --> 00:03:36,083
Hey. What're you
guys doing in here?

39
00:03:36,166 --> 00:03:39,750
Tsukimi! Stop her...
She's completely off her nut!

40
00:03:39,833 --> 00:03:42,875
Oh... you're awake.
Is your fever any better?

41
00:03:43,625 --> 00:03:45,166
Fever?

42
00:03:45,250 --> 00:03:48,583
Oh, that's right, I was
a little sick last night.

43
00:03:48,666 --> 00:03:51,333
Wait, but how does he know?

44
00:03:51,416 --> 00:03:54,250
Technology! Let's
start over here.

45
