Fabric! Rhinestones!
And lace and beads!

47
00:03:59,333 --> 00:04:00,458
O-kay...

48
00:04:00,541 --> 00:04:01,833
Come on, let's do it!

49
00:04:01,916 --> 00:04:03,916
Let's do what? I'm lost.

50
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:08,375
Cryin' out loud! I told you,
we're going to make this!

51
00:04:09,333 --> 00:04:12,458
You want to make
a jelly? A flower hat?

52
00:04:12,541 --> 00:04:14,666
Hel-lo?! The dress!

53
