103
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:21,125
Yes... unfortunately.

104
00:06:21,208 --> 00:06:23,666
But where will I
live? It's my home.

105
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:25,708
I've got nowhere else to go!

106
00:06:25,791 --> 00:06:29,833
It'll be all right, Tsukimi.
We can make a home together!

107
00:06:30,583 --> 00:06:31,833
Together?

108
00:06:33,125 --> 00:06:35,375
We can rent a little
house by the shore.

109
00:06:35,458 --> 00:06:37,875
We'll live a humble,
quiet life together

110
00:06:37,958 --> 00:06:40,291
just watching the jellyfish.

111
00:07:01,958 --> 00:07:03,291
That'll never happen.

112
00:07:03,375 --> 00:07:06,541
Y'see... she won't forgive
you having sex with me.

113
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,000
I'm sorry!

114
00:07:13,958 --> 00:07:15,541
Tsukimi Kurashita, huh.

115
00:07:15,625 --> 00:07:18,916
Mhm. Mr. Koibuchi insisted.

116
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:22,166
Shu's gone... he leaves
tonight to go overseas...

117
00:07:22,250 --> 00:07:23,875
so he won't find out.

118
00:07:23,958 --> 00:07:28,041
So you don't got a photo?
How about an address?

119
00:07:36,375 --> 00:07:38,500
H-How many
meters did you buy?

120
00:07:38,583 --> 00:07:40,958
I don't know, I just
bought the whole bolt.

121
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:43,333
Let's cut the sucker up.

122
00:07:43,416 --> 00:07:45,833
Are you sure that's
the right way to start?

123
00:07:45,916 --> 00:07:48,916
No clue. But we've
gotta start somewhere.

124
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,458
But isn't cutting a little
permanent? Just because you're

125
00:07:51,541 --> 00:07:54,041
