you know how to make clothes.

126
00:07:54,125 --> 00:07:56,625
Well no, but I wear
them all the time.

127
00:07:57,916 --> 00:07:58,875
Banzai!

128
00:07:58,958 --> 00:08:00,708
Fabric faceplant!

129
00:08:00,791 --> 00:08:02,166
Iketani!

130
00:08:03,333 --> 00:08:04,750
Look I'm a salmon roll or...

