185
00:10:42,208 --> 00:10:45,708
That's because you insisted we
have the mango flan for dessert.

186
00:10:45,791 --> 00:10:48,875
Right... Let's pay our respects
to the spirit of Guan Yu...

187
00:10:48,958 --> 00:10:51,333
then get squeaky
clean at the public bath.

188
00:10:51,416 --> 00:10:52,541
How cool!

189
00:10:54,166 --> 00:10:56,500
That afro is totally righteous.

190
00:10:56,583 --> 00:10:59,541
It's like, the way
biggest I've ever seen.

191
00:10:59,625 --> 00:11:02,833
Do you mind if I touch it?
Omigod I already am touching it!

192
00:11:02,916 --> 00:11:05,041
It's a Stylish!

193
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:07,625
Picture time... smile!

194
00:11:08,416 --> 00:11:11,041
Listen up, you two.
There's no reason to try

195
00:11:11,125 --> 00:11:14,083
and spare your feelings on
this. You've killed any chance

196
00:11:14,166 --> 00:11:17,375
