No need to cut us
down right when we're

198
00:11:19,125 --> 00:11:22,000
beginning to get
motivated. That's not cool.

199
00:11:22,083 --> 00:11:24,291
Well... let me
see what I can do...

200
00:11:25,750 --> 00:11:27,750
