Yuck... How dare you
give my haute couture skirt

203
00:11:32,083 --> 00:11:33,333
an elastic waistband?!

204
00:11:33,416 --> 00:11:35,916
Hush now... Just
try it on this way.

205
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,541
Really?

206
00:11:37,625 --> 00:11:40,583
This spring... Rock the "poor
pauper" look in a dorky skirt

207
00:11:40,666 --> 00:11:42,625
with an elastic waistband!

208
00:11:42,708 --> 00:11:44,333
No! Nooo!

209
00:11:44,416 --> 00:11:46,708
It should be way flouncier!

210
00:11:46,791 --> 00:11:49,458
With the pattern you cut...
there's no way it could be!

211
00:11:49,541 --> 00:11:51,000
Oh, man...

212
00:11:51,083 --> 00:11:54,208
It's wrong! That pathetic piece
of cloth isn't even close to

213
00:11:54,291 --> 00:11:56,000
expressing an inch
of the delicate beauty

214
00:11:56,083 --> 00:11:57,416
of the Flower Hat Jelly!

215
00:11:57,500 --> 00:12:00,583
