nanometer of the awesomeness!

216
00:12:00,666 --> 00:12:04,333
My god... The otaku girl
rant has been unleashed.

217
00:12:05,375 --> 00:12:07,541
To start with, the bells
of all jellyfish, not just

218
00:12:07,625 --> 00:12:09,583
the Flower Hat Jelly,
contain a fluidity of

219
00:12:09,666 --> 00:12:12,125
motion requisite to
their body structure.

220
00:12:15,208 --> 00:12:18,500
If that's what you want,
I'll just disappear.

221
00:12:18,583 --> 00:12:21,708
